OL,5,G0005 The Emergency Ward
OL,6,     FAt The Royal Melbourne Hospital's
OL,7,     Fmajor trauma centre, Dr Taylor's
OL,8,     Fpatient deteriorates with a
OL,9,     Fsuspected brain bleed. Dr Tristan
OL,10,     FHarding straightens a young man's
OL,11,     Fdislocated ankle.
OL,12,G0110 24 Hours in A&E
OL,13,     FJames is rushed to St George's
OL,14,     Fafter a head-on car crash.
OL,15,     FMargaret's had a fall, but her
OL,16,     Fdaughter has tales to tell of her
OL,17,     Fmother's adventurous life in
OL,18,     FLondon in the swinging 60s.
